section.section:
The criteria shall provide a basis for the priority ranking of projects, and shall include:
The financial capacity and fiscal accountability of the applicant;
The location of the underground storage tank and the degree to which removal of the tank would impose a geographical hardship on the surrounding community or industries dependent on availability of the petroleum;
The extent to which the existence of the tank is required for an essential public service;
Previous efforts expended to correct any existing environmental problem and to maintain compliance with State and federal regulations;
Measures to assure accountability for all funds awarded under this subtitle; and
Any other criteria that the Secretary considers appropriate.
